Now that we have one less `GetLocator` call, [the only remaining one](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/master/src/validation.cpp#L2917) can also be inlined to `GetLocator(m_chain.Tip())` (we're already holding `cs_main`)

```patch
